title: Bug 116564 - Hyperlink builder title changes with settings
description: The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', but it changes based on the settings.
OB: When I click on 'OK' and reopen the hyperlink builder, the title becomes 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', regardless of the settings.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'.
2. Click on 'OK'.
3. Reopen the hyperlink builder.
